IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: THE BLUE BARN THEATRE EXISTS TO ENHANCE THE CULTURAL LIFE OF OMAHA, NEBRASKA AND SURROUNDING COMMUNITIES BY PRODUCING PROFESSIONALLY-EXECUTED LIVE THEATRE PERFORMANCES.
IRS990.MissionDesc: THE BLUE BARN THEATRE EXISTS TO ENHANCE THE CULTURAL LIFE OF OMAHA, NEBRASKA AND SURROUNDING COMMUNITIES BY PRODUCING PROFESSIONALLY-EXECUTED LIVE THEATRE PERFORMANCES.
IRS990.Desc: WE PROVIDE THE COMMUNITY OF OMAHA, NEBRASKA AND SURROUNDING REGION WITH A QUALITY ENSEMBLE ACTING COMPANY. DURING THE YEAR WE PRODUCED 3 SHOWS AND 4 SPECIAL EVENTS WITH A TOTAL OF 51 PERFORMANCES. THE TOTAL ATTENDANCE FOR THE YEAR WAS 5220 PEOPLE WITH SOME VIRTUALLY FOR THE SPECIAL EVENTS.
